    "The objective is to discover hidden patterns, relationships, or structures within the data.",
    "Common unsupervised learning techniques include Bayesian networks, hidden Markov models and clustering algorithms such as K-means or hierarchical clustering.",
    "Typical applications are clustering processes, e.g.",
    "for customer segmentation or in healthcare to gain a better understanding in diagnosis, prevention and treatment of diseases.",
    "\"Reinforcement learning\" is a further category of machine learning in which intelligent agents attempt to optimise an output through a given incentive system."
